data.description: SELLER IS WILLING TO PAY $5,000 OF BUYERS CLOSING COSTS! Welcome to this four bedroom twin home located in north Mandan. Upon entering the main floor you notice the vaulted ceilings in the living room and dining room opening up into the kitchen and a patio door to the backyard with concrete patio. The main floor also features a full bathroom, laundry room, second bedroom, and the primary suite featuring a full bathroom and walkin closet. The basement offers a spacious family room, two additional bedrooms and an unfinished bathroom. The home also has a two stall garage, and a fully fenced backyard. Call a REALTOR today to schedule a private showing.
